I will never leave you and I will never forsake you.

01:16:28.571 --> 01:16:33.360
Lo, until the end of the earth I will be with you always.

01:16:33.360 --> 01:16:37.840
' But a shaking is coming to your shore.

01:16:37.840 --> 01:16:40.500
A shaking is coming to Europe.

01:16:40.500 --> 01:16:57.897
A shaking is coming to the lands of this earth through the signs of the heaven.

01:16:57.897 --> 01:17:45.162
There'll be a shaking in politics, in war, in finances, and a shaking in the heavens and in the earth.

01:17:45.162 --> 01:18:21.540
But every one of these vast shakings is designed to bring in my fruit.

01:18:21.540 --> 01:18:25.143
For I have long patience for it.

01:18:25.143 --> 01:18:28.440
I'm not out of patience.

01:18:28.440 --> 01:18:30.170
I'm out of time.

01:18:30.170 --> 01:18:31.897
The time is short.

01:18:31.897 --> 01:18:40.879
He's not out of patience; He has long patience, but I'm out of time.

01:18:51.138 --> 01:18:51.440
You hear what the Spirit of the Lord said?

01:18:51.830 --> 01:18:55.736
He just said that very loud to me.

01:18:55.736 --> 01:18:59.260
He said, 'I'm not out of patience.

01:19:09.160 --> 01:19:09.460
I have long patience, but I'm out of time.

01:19:09.460 --> 01:19:25.831
This dispensation of grace, this dispensation of time has come to an end and I've given you a sliver more to bring in my fruit.

01:19:25.831 --> 01:19:30.194
One last call I call you forth.

01:19:30.194 --> 01:19:34.429
One last opportunity to get on the boat.

01:19:34.1000 --> 01:19:39.280
For as in the days of Noah, so will it be.

01:19:39.280 --> 01:19:42.124
Noah got on the boat.

01:19:42.124 --> 01:19:43.760
Will you get on the boat?

01:19:52.160 --> 01:19:52.520
This is one last call.

01:19:52.520 --> 01:20:00.347
Just like I said before, one last call for a harvest.

01:20:00.347 --> 01:20:07.093
For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:20:07.093 --> 01:20:08.640
Find a scripture.

01:20:08.640 --> 01:20:09.783
I hear him.

01:20:09.783 --> 01:20:12.920
Wide is the way to destruction and narrow...

01:20:12.920 --> 01:20:15.634
Enter ye in at the Strait gate.

01:21:49.799 --> 01:21:49.1000
For wide is the gate and broad is the way that leads to destruction, and many there be which go in there.

01:21:49.1000 --> 01:22:00.120
Because Strait is the gate, and narrow is the way, which leads unto life, and few there be that find it.

01:22:00.120 --> 01:22:01.560
' Matthew 7:13-14.

01:22:01.560 --> 01:22:05.066
He doesn't want that any should perish.

01:22:05.066 --> 01:22:08.240
Ladies and gentlemen, God has long patience.

01:22:08.240 --> 01:22:12.926
But God's not out of patience; He's out of time.

01:22:12.926 --> 01:22:16.960
He says, 'A great shaking now is coming.

01:22:16.960 --> 01:22:52.063
For I have yelled and I have yelled and I have yelled and I gave you a chance even through COVID to shake the church, and yet you go back into your slumber.

01:22:52.063 --> 01:22:56.380
' Many went back into their slumber.

01:22:56.380 --> 01:23:39.773
COVID was a wakeup call upon the nations.

01:23:39.773 --> 01:23:51.880
I shook at the shaking of the nations; it went through the nations.

01:23:54.940 --> 01:23:57.139
And therefore, there will be a second round of great shaking.

01:24:10.467 --> 01:24:11.173
And this shaking will be the last shaking.

01:24:11.173 --> 01:24:22.576
A shaking that will shake the world—one last call, one last time.

01:24:22.576 --> 01:24:31.690
A new, great wave that will be greater, that will dwarf the first wave.

01:24:31.690 --> 01:25:00.395
A wave that will shake this world one last time, one last call.

01:25:00.395 --> 01:25:08.159
For I'm bringing you as the bride to my side.

01:25:08.159 --> 01:25:18.239
For they woke for a split minute and went back to sleep.

01:25:18.239 --> 01:25:24.1000
Many are not ready or prepared for what you're about to see.

01:25:24.1000 --> 01:25:29.030
I've warned you to come by my side.

01:25:29.030 --> 01:25:36.408
He said, 'All of you must come up higher.

01:25:36.408 --> 01:25:44.569
It's time to come up higher, for great sobering days are upon you.

01:25:44.569 --> 01:25:52.060
' But the true bride, the remnant that I have brought to my side, will do great and mighty works.

01:25:52.060 --> 01:25:59.920
They will do great and mighty things, bringing in my harvest.

01:25:59.920 --> 01:26:11.440
That covering of my blood, that glory covering, will be over you, and the death angel will pass before you and it will not touch you.

01:26:11.440 --> 01:26:13.040
Fear not, church.

01:26:13.040 --> 01:26:15.600
Keep your eyes upon me.

01:26:15.600 --> 01:26:16.680
Be bold.

01:26:16.680 --> 01:26:24.239
He's talking about Joshua, I believe: 'Have I not commanded you?

01:26:24.239 --> 01:26:28.533
Be strong and courageous.

01:26:28.533 --> 01:26:38.980
Do not be afraid; do not be discouraged, for the Lord your God will be with you wherever you go.

01:26:38.980 --> 01:26:55.253
' Be not afraid, church, for what you're about to see, for a great shaking is coming, and many are not prepared for what you're about to see.

01:26:55.253 --> 01:26:58.107
He said many will die.

01:26:58.107 --> 01:27:01.480
Come up higher in your word level.

01:27:01.480 --> 01:27:05.387
Come up higher in your drinking level.

01:27:05.387 --> 01:27:08.651
Drink of me; drink from the well.

01:27:08.651 --> 01:27:11.910
I see New York in the warm months.

01:27:11.910 --> 01:27:15.280
I see the buildings and the sun shining.

01:27:27.707 --> 01:27:28.120
It's a hope.

01:27:28.120 --> 01:27:33.028
You'll see a great harvest even in just one day.

01:27:50.840 --> 01:27:51.189
You'll see vast amounts of souls in just one day, for I'm bringing them in across the land.

01:27:51.189 --> 01:27:53.640
I see Asia shaking in a day.

01:27:53.640 --> 01:27:56.426
The earth will tremble and shake.

01:27:56.426 --> 01:28:00.228
It will rock and reel like a drunkard.

01:28:01.099 --> 01:28:22.586
The earth shall reel to and fro like a drunkard and shall be removed like a hut; its transgression shall be heavy upon it, and it shall fall and not rise again.

01:28:30.388 --> 01:28:30.639
That's Isaiah 24.

01:28:30.639 --> 01:28:36.879
I have to read the whole chapter on that one.

01:28:36.879 --> 01:28:40.280
Many will know it's time to go.

01:28:40.280 --> 01:28:42.639
There will be a great flow.

01:28:51.550 --> 01:28:51.880
I see Africa.

01:28:52.539 --> 01:29:04.008
I see a light that is shining all over Africa, and I see a great harvest of souls—a sea of people from tribes of every kind.

01:29:04.008 --> 01:29:16.983
They're coming to the saving knowledge of the Lord Jesus Christ, and it's spread throughout Africa, people of all kinds of different shades of skin.

01:29:16.983 --> 01:29:21.280
They are giving their hearts like Reinhard Bonnke.

01:29:21.280 --> 01:29:27.667
A major harvest of souls is coming to Africa with healings, signs, and wonders.

01:29:40.159 --> 01:29:40.400
I see the sun setting again.

01:29:40.400 --> 01:29:44.850
This dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

01:29:44.850 --> 01:29:48.099
Jesus is standing at the door.

01:29:48.099 --> 01:29:52.239
Oh, how I love Jesus because he first loved me.

01:29:52.559 --> 01:29:54.160
The King is here.

01:29:54.160 --> 01:29:56.311
We're calling in the harvest.

01:30:04.980 --> 01:30:05.320
A shaking is coming to the nations.

01:30:06.327 --> 01:30:08.618
It will happen in a 24-hour period.

01:30:08.618 --> 01:30:11.964
Everything you know is about to change.

01:30:11.964 --> 01:30:20.809
When you see it, it will be the waterfall edge—an acceleration of the labor pains upon this earth.

01:30:20.809 --> 01:30:32.239
As you enter into the next Jewish feast day, I believe he's talking about Passover, you're going to see an acceleration.

01:30:32.239 --> 01:30:36.039
I am releasing the angelic host, these warring angels.

01:30:36.039 --> 01:30:38.239
I see them dumping out of heaven.

01:30:38.239 --> 01:30:44.222
There'll be two on each side of these unsaved loved ones.

01:30:44.222 --> 01:30:53.840
They will have to flatly reject me, but it will be uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:30:53.840 --> 01:30:55.813
I see two angels.

01:30:57.679 --> 01:31:00.260
He said, 'I'm sending my angels and it gives them freedom to make the choice.

01:31:00.260 --> 01:31:11.669
' I see the harvest and the souls, and the angelic host are warring on our behalf.

01:31:12.249 --> 01:31:18.853
He said, 'I wish that none should perish, but all come to repentance.

01:31:18.853 --> 01:31:23.600
' I see the angelic host warring on our behalf.

01:31:23.600 --> 01:31:24.960
They're flooding North Korea right now.

01:31:30.034 --> 01:31:30.262
The angels of the Lord are warring on our behalf.

01:31:37.660 --> 01:31:37.930
The Lord has sent his warring angels, for there are more with us than there are with them.

01:31:37.930 --> 01:31:41.610
You'll see creative signs and wonders will follow them that believe.

01:31:41.610 --> 01:31:47.827
This will be shock and awe to the world, for heaven and earth are going to collide.

01:31:47.827 --> 01:31:58.933
It will be just like Brother Hagin gave the word—as easy as a fish swimming through the water or a bird flying in the air.

01:32:09.199 --> 01:32:09.489
Like you taking your next breath, you'll tap into the spirit realm effortlessly.

01:32:22.533 --> 01:32:22.840
You'll step over, walking in the supernatural.

01:32:22.840 --> 01:32:26.320
Where sin abounds, grace does much more abound.

01:32:35.280 --> 01:32:35.502
But a shaking is coming.

01:32:35.502 --> 01:32:41.129
We thank you, Lord, for all that you have in store.

01:32:41.129 --> 01:32:44.411
Father, regarding the crypto laws, we'll lack no good thing.

01:32:44.411 --> 01:32:51.439
We'll have more than enough to get the job done.

01:32:51.439 --> 01:33:07.199
Thank you, Lord, that we're hearing you on what we're supposed to do with our finances, that we'll obey you and know exactly what to do to bring in the money towards the harvest.

01:33:07.199 --> 01:33:11.040
Stretch that dollar to bring in the greatest harvest.

01:33:11.040 --> 01:33:12.926
It's all about the harvest.

01:33:12.926 --> 01:33:16.560
Lateness of the hour.

01:33:17.670 --> 01:33:19.150
For great days to come.

01:33:19.150 --> 01:33:21.509
Great days for the church.

01:33:22.978 --> 01:33:23.262
A great day.

01:33:33.970 --> 01:33:34.200
He knows our idea of what's great and what his is about: harvest.

01:33:34.200 --> 01:33:38.720
Days of fun have just begun.

01:33:38.720 --> 01:33:44.590
Seeing the healing and manifestation of his glory on people; that's what he's all about.

01:33:44.590 --> 01:33:51.880
People get all excited about finances and new things like that, but God's treasure is people.

01:33:51.880 --> 01:33:54.267
His treasure is his children.

01:33:54.267 --> 01:33:58.019
His streets are paved with gold, ladies and gentlemen.

01:34:04.080 --> 01:34:04.320
He doesn't get excited about finances.

01:34:04.320 --> 01:34:09.960
He gets excited when one of us turns and says, "Hey, I want you, Jesus.

01:34:22.439 --> 01:34:22.639
" He gets excited that just one of us comes to Jesus.

01:34:22.639 --> 01:34:24.800
He's excited when his kids say yes.

01:34:24.800 --> 01:34:28.000
His heart is the harvest.

01:34:28.000 --> 01:34:30.400
His heart is a father's heart.

01:34:34.240 --> 01:34:35.307
I don't want to see any of my kids go to hell.

01:34:35.307 --> 01:34:36.527
His heart is the harvest.

01:34:36.527 --> 01:34:44.100
Like any really good father, you don't want to see any of your kids get in harm's way, pain, or suffering.

01:34:44.100 --> 01:34:45.920
I want good things, right?

01:34:48.159 --> 01:34:50.363
And that's where his heart is right now for the harvest.

01:34:50.363 --> 01:34:56.347
He's saying, "I'm calling them out of the darkness and into the light.

01:35:08.036 --> 01:35:08.204
I want to help them, Diana, with all my might.

01:35:17.360 --> 01:35:17.531
" If that's what's important to him, it's important to me.

01:35:20.520 --> 01:35:20.800
If this is important to God, it's important to me.

01:35:20.800 --> 01:35:24.423
Help me, Lord, help you.

01:35:24.423 --> 01:35:34.040
Anoint me in a special way to bring them in by the boatloads—a big old shrimping net dredging the bottom.

01:35:34.040 --> 01:35:36.480
We're going to bring them in.

01:35:36.480 --> 01:35:37.679
They're coming in hot.

01:35:37.679 --> 01:35:42.380
Thank you, Lord, for we made it through another week.

01:35:42.380 --> 01:35:47.680
As we go into this weekend, let people be refreshed, Lord.

01:35:47.680 --> 01:35:57.040
Let them come up higher in their prayer life with you, finding a good church to get involved in.

01:35:57.040 --> 01:36:02.217
They know where the revival is going to take place: churches.

01:36:02.217 --> 01:36:10.151
Raise up new pastors that are ready to finish the race.

01:36:10.151 --> 01:36:14.982
Raise up people that have integrity with what they've been given.

01:36:27.151 --> 01:36:27.407
Have an integrity of anointing where they always attract to deflect, keeping their eyes on you, Jesus.

01:36:27.407 --> 01:36:28.431
We're going vertical.

01:36:28.431 --> 01:36:29.746
Thank you, Lord.

01:36:29.746 --> 01:36:39.199
And as I say this, I see Rome again; I see the Vatican; I see the Catholic Church.

01:36:39.199 --> 01:36:44.906
You'll see the antichrist agenda on another scale in the days ahead rising up.

01:36:44.906 --> 01:36:51.760
They know the time we're in, and they're going to rise up at another level.

01:36:51.760 --> 01:37:03.706
The antichrist agenda is going to rise up at another level: Oppression, religious efforts trying to suppress freedom of speech in Europe and Canada.

01:37:03.706 --> 01:37:08.906
More pressure and persecution are coming on the church because they know the time is short.

01:37:14.990 --> 01:37:16.469
The enemy knows the time is short, and he's coming more viciously than ever before.

01:37:16.469 --> 01:37:22.440
Hold fast to this open door of opportunity.

01:37:29.211 --> 01:37:29.429
Be contenders.

01:37:30.580 --> 01:37:33.830
I see the church holding up their hands and saying, "Not yet.

01:37:33.830 --> 01:37:37.028
You can't do this yet.

01:37:37.028 --> 01:37:42.720
" We're holding our hand like a police officer directing traffic.

01:37:42.720 --> 01:37:43.560
Not yet.

01:37:43.560 --> 01:37:46.060
We have authority over you, and it's not yet.

01:37:46.060 --> 01:37:48.987
It's going to try to really amp it up to escalate the end times.

01:37:48.987 --> 01:37:56.123
I see a war breaking out at a greater level in the Middle East and in Europe.

01:37:56.123 --> 01:38:02.194
This is like what I'm talking about: portals of CERN and all these other things.

01:38:05.529 --> 01:38:08.411
And I see the church, the remnant; we're going to get a harvest.

01:38:10.959 --> 01:38:17.400
A shaking and labor pains are going to come on even greater, and the harvest will come out of the shaking and the great labor pains.

01:38:23.695 --> 01:38:24.159
You understand, lover?

01:38:24.159 --> 01:38:26.032
That's what I see.

01:38:26.032 --> 01:38:34.040
Even telling it to stop, it's still going on in labor pains.

01:38:39.440 --> 01:38:41.291
It's holding back that antichrist spirit from taking over completely, saying, "We're holding you back through prayer.

01:38:48.650 --> 01:38:49.020
" And I see a shaking of the earth's crust.

01:38:49.020 --> 01:38:56.453
But this is actual hell on earth, like a great tribulation.

01:39:11.456 --> 01:39:11.904
And the church is pushing back through prayer.

01:39:11.904 --> 01:39:20.180
But because of the time, the window is getting smaller and smaller.

01:39:20.180 --> 01:39:29.299
There's not much time to push back because the time is getting shorter and shorter.

01:39:36.560 --> 01:39:36.907
And the church is pushing against it.

01:39:36.907 --> 01:39:39.332
We want the harvest; bring it in.

01:40:02.069 --> 01:40:02.697
And the glorious church is moving, and the time's getting shorter and shorter—we're out of time.

01:40:02.697 --> 01:40:06.230
We're at God's mercy.

01:40:06.230 --> 01:40:10.260
It's about what's been set in the spirit realm.

01:40:18.766 --> 01:40:22.400
The church is pushing back, and in the middle, there's a collision, and you're seeing it, and the harvest is coming in.

01:40:22.400 --> 01:40:28.920
But now you'll see the labor pains because of what's been said in the Word.

01:40:28.920 --> 01:40:32.686
Labor pains, boom, boom, boom.

01:40:32.686 --> 01:40:42.434
And the church is pushing back, and the prayer and all of it is happening so fast—acceleration.

01:40:42.434 --> 01:40:46.559
That's what he said: acceleration of labor pains.

01:40:46.559 --> 01:40:46.960
Hallelujah.

01:40:46.960 --> 01:41:00.604
But the bottom line of where we are right now is that if you're here tonight and you've never asked Jesus Christ to be your Lord and personal Savior, that's all that matters.

01:41:00.604 --> 01:41:03.140
You're not ready; you're not prepared for the shaking.

01:41:14.023 --> 01:41:16.856
He's talking about supplies and certain things he's instructed you to do.

01:41:16.856 --> 01:41:22.046
Maybe he's instructed you to get some extra bottled water or some medical bandages.

01:41:22.046 --> 01:41:25.097
I'm just throwing something out there.

01:41:25.097 --> 01:41:39.280
But whatever he's told you to do, just like at the marriage feast, he didn't take the wine and bring it out of nothing; he turned water into wine.

01:41:39.280 --> 01:41:41.079
He worked with something.

01:41:41.079 --> 01:41:44.320
He had the fishes and the loaves and then he multiplied it.

01:41:44.320 --> 01:41:47.253
He took what you had and he made it into something special.

01:41:47.253 --> 01:41:50.480
That's why I believe so wholeheartedly in tithing and giving to your local church.

01:42:01.250 --> 01:42:01.520
God will take, like he did for the widow lady with the little bit of meal and the olive oil, and he blessed her.

01:42:03.840 --> 01:42:08.514
But because of her obedience to give out of her sacrifice, God took a little and made it into a lot.

01:42:08.514 --> 01:42:19.246
He had to get it out of her hand and have her be fully persuaded that what he has promised, he's able also to perform.

01:42:19.246 --> 01:42:24.057
In these end times, what is he telling you to do?

01:42:24.057 --> 01:42:26.583
Mary said, "Whatever he tells you to do, do it.

01:42:26.583 --> 01:42:37.980
" Don't just sit back and go, "Well, I'm waiting on my blessed assurance that God's just going to do everything and just bring it like ripe cherries off the tree.

01:42:39.430 --> 01:42:41.189
" You have to go out and make something happen, folks.

01:42:41.189 --> 01:42:45.867
Stop waiting for God always to just show up with some miracle.

01:42:45.867 --> 01:42:49.460
Whatever you have in your hand to do, do it.

01:42:49.460 --> 01:43:02.533
It may just be a little bit of cake and oil, but whatever he tells you to do, if he says bring the water in, I'm going to turn the water into wine.

01:43:11.226 --> 01:43:11.493
If that's your case, then follow the leading of the Holy Ghost.

01:43:11.493 --> 01:43:15.280
Faith without works is dead.

01:43:15.280 --> 01:43:20.320
Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

01:43:23.189 --> 01:43:26.651
For those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons of God.

01:43:30.104 --> 01:43:30.352
I believe we will be led by the Spirit of God.

01:43:36.461 --> 01:43:36.719
You said, "Well, I'm looking for an audible voice.

01:43:36.719 --> 01:43:42.777
" You're going to get snared by a demonic spirit because that's not usually the way that God speaks.

01:43:43.863 --> 01:43:45.324
I know of one time He spoke.

01:43:45.324 --> 01:43:54.800
He said, "This is my beloved Son, in whom I am well pleased," and the dove came—the anointing came on like a dove.

01:43:54.800 --> 01:43:59.620
John the Baptist and all heard it and they said, "I hear Jesus.

01:43:59.620 --> 01:44:02.750
I heard the Lord say it.

01:44:02.750 --> 01:44:08.520
" But it was not something He did all the time.

01:44:08.520 --> 01:44:14.400
It's the still small voice He leads us by.

01:44:18.640 --> 01:44:20.560
For those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons of God.

01:44:20.560 --> 01:44:23.982
He speaks through that still small voice.

01:44:23.982 --> 01:44:26.520
Stop looking for some audible, earth-shaking voice.

01:44:26.520 --> 01:44:32.651
You're looking and saying, "I'm waiting," and He's like, "I'm speaking to you on the inside.

01:44:32.651 --> 01:44:35.573
" Get familiar with Him by reading His word.

01:44:35.573 --> 01:44:38.440
He'll speak to you in His word.

01:44:40.267 --> 01:44:45.199
That word will become life to you, and you'll become sensitive to what He's saying to do.

01:44:45.199 --> 01:44:52.779
So whatever He tells you to do, like Mary said to the servants, "Go and get the water and fill it up.

01:44:52.779 --> 01:44:55.520
" Jesus said it; do it.

01:44:59.867 --> 01:45:08.719
It wasn't that He just looked at the pots that were empty and said, "Wine, be.

01:45:08.719 --> 01:45:20.799
Go fill it up and then I'll do something," but He wants your participation in it.

01:45:20.799 --> 01:45:21.440
Do you understand?

01:45:21.440 --> 01:45:22.211
We're co-laborers with Christ.

01:45:22.211 --> 01:45:22.735
He wants your participation in it.

01:45:22.735 --> 01:45:23.182
What are you going to do?

01:45:23.182 --> 01:45:23.520
Faith without works is dead.

01:45:23.520 --> 01:45:25.970
What did He tell you to do?

01:45:23.520 --> 01:45:23.840
